news.title: Tom Dunne elected Chairperson of IMRO
news.summary: Dunne will take over from current Chair Eleanor McEvoy in May next year.

news.title: All Together Now announce KNEECAP as first headliner for 2026 festival

news.title: The Wolfe Tones to return to 3Arena next July
news.summary: They will play two dates on July 3 and 4.
